<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para>The constructor initialize the context variables of the MBEDTLS library by calling the functions mbedtls_pk_init and mbedtls_ctr_drbg_init. Afterwards it enables the the entropy hardware for the usage of the random subsystem with the entropy API. By calling the function mbedtls_ctr_drbg_seed with an entropy function a seed will be generated for the further usage by the cryptografic services. </para>
